overview:
Futonic is a search engine optimization (SEO) and online marketing consultancy.

Futonic.co.uk is a SEO and specialist online marketing service based in the south west of England based in Wiltshire. Futonic started out several years ago as Juggle Media, which key focus was in the affiliate marketing sector as is still going from strength to strength year on year. Futonic was started in late 2008 by Matthew Weeks, a young entrepreneur and investor. Matthew designed and marketed niche website for many years and got some great results through trial and error. Learning the hard way is sometimes considered to be the best way to learn.
